    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>to a large pot with a lid over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>ground coriander </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
