        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>,<strong> </strong>then cut into 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>strips per person</p><p>Add the <strong>pastry strips </strong>to a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Spread your <strong>mango chutney</strong> over one side of each strip and sprinkle your <strong>nigella seeds </strong>on top</p><p>Twist each<strong> </strong>pastry strip from the ends in opposite directions until they look like a spiral</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
