        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven and cook the pastry twists for 6-8 min or until puffed up and golden – these are your <strong>chutney twists</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, heat a small dry pan over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
