    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, remove the pot from the heat and blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>cultured coconut </strong>and most<strong> </strong>of the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save some for garnish!)</p><p>Season to taste with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>carrot & coriander soup</strong></p>",
