      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>carrot & coriander soup </strong>with the <strong>chutney twists </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the soup with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>almonds </strong>and the <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
